flowRoot.flowPara: Composed of many time-lapsed frames of atom data.
50~80% of which is water, compression is necessary.
Through user experiments, 8 bit quantisation is recommended for visual fidelity.
Our Water Compression performs best: up to 11% gain over next best scheme.
Delta Coding Interframe Compression performs best: ≈10% at 8-bit quantisation.
Created a predictive point cloud compressor with predictors based on water.
Compared against four existing intraframe schemes.
Five Interframe Compression Schemes tested on several datasets.
Datasets chosen based on coherency of motion and overall size.
Convert floating point data to integer data.
Visualiser constructed to conduct quantisation experiment.
